                <head>21. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On January 13, 1962, the Joint Chiefs of Staff transmitted to Secretary <persName
                        corresp="#p_MNRS1">McNamara</persName>
                    <gloss target="#t_JCSM1">JCSM</gloss>-33-62, which in 14 numbered paragraphs
                    stated the strategic importance of the Southeast Asia mainland. For text, see
                        <hi rend="italic">United States-Vietnam Relations, 1945-1967</hi>, Book 12,
                    pages 448-454.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
